subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Stock-car race tracks outside Los Angeles and Atlanta each lost one of their two annual races in the 36-race 2011 Sprint Cup Series schedule, which was released Wednesday.
